 Inderal (propranolol), a beta-blocker, can prevent the physical symptoms of anxiety that \
 occur with social phobia. \
\
 II. PRESUMED MECHANISM OF ACTION \
\
 Benzodiazepines facilitate GABA's ability to bind to its receptor site, enhancing the effects \
 of GABA. GABA is the major inhibitory neurotransmitter in the brain, and increasing \
 GABA results in reduced anxiety, increased sedation, muscle relaxation, and reduction in \
 seizures. \
\
