\
 Possible side effects associated with Buspar include dizziness, headache, nausea, \
 lightheadedness, excitement, and insomnia. \
\
 Although beta-blockers are generally well tolerated, they can cause a variety of side effects. \
 They can cause sexual dysfunction, with up to 10% of male patients developing impotence \
 on certain beta-blockers. They can also cause fatigue, dizziness, shortness of breath, \
 angina, cold hands and feet, difficulty sleeping, and nightmares. \
