more than performance. By contrast, job enrichment is accomplished by increasing \
responsibilities (vertical loading), and results in increased satisfaction and performance, as \
well as decreased turnover and absenteeism. Individual preferences for job enrichment \
exist, with those in favor of it tending to be high in growth-need strength, knowledge and \
