stands for LInear Structural RELations, is one type of structural equation modeling. \
LISREL makes distinctions between independent and dependent variables in addition to \
latent (unobserved) and manifest variables. LISREL looks at both direct and indirect \
effects, as well as both unidirectional and bi-directional paths. \
