>TEST TRYOUT During test tryout, the developer tries out all the items on the available \
sample. \
\
>ITEM ANALYSIS In the item analysis phase, each item is analyzed in a variety of ways \
with the goal of deciding which items are best and should be kept. Items are analyzed in \
terms of item difficulty, item discrimination, and item validity. Item-characteristic curves \
are also constructed. \
\
