>MULTICULTURALISM/CULTURAL DIVERSITY     Early models of minority \
mental health considered people from minority racial or cultural groups to be genetically \
deficient or culturally disadvantaged. The currently favored model. multiculturalism. \
considers all racial and ethnic groups to be on an equal level. White middle-class culture \
is no longer considered the yardstick by which all other cultures should be measured. \
