by discomfort with and reduced capacity for close relationships, as well as by peculiarities \
in cognition, perception, ideation, appearance and behavior, as evidenced by five or more \
of the following: ideas of reference; odd beliefs (e.g., telepathy, clairvoyance); unusual \
