perfectionism that interferes with task completion; excessive focus on work and \
productivity to the exclusion of friendship and leisure; overconscientiousness and \
inflexibility about morals and values; inability to discard worn-out and worthless objects; \
reluctance to delegate tasks to others; stingy with money; rigid and stubborn. \
